Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息日的早上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.37,0:00:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就這麼偉大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩服佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只掃了一下門口結果掃到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便而已  我想就一起掃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有在休息天才能早起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.55,0:01:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只睡在被窩裡就太浪費時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吉野屋老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦  宮子同學  由乃同學
